#
#   Main menu implemented on top of the fuzzel frontend.

#   Made at and for omarchy-mac
#   (Omarchy fork for Apple Silicon Macs, link in the readme)
#   Uses fuzzel as the launcher frontend on aarch64.

#   TayoWrld
#    .-|:"""":""""""'''"""":|-.
#   :  |'----'-------------'|  :
